  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-focus-ring\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-focus-ring/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `get_design_tokens`, `find_components_using_token`\n- **Report wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Ring color, width, offset, border-radius. Dark mode. High contrast mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Focus indicator visibility (3:1 contrast ratio minimum per WCAG 2.4.11). :focus-visible support. Reduced-motion.\n3. **Functionality** — Attach to any focusable element. Keyboard-only focus detection. Custom ring styling. Inset vs outset.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. Integration with other components' focus states. CSS Parts.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — All API documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Focus/blur. Keyboard vs mouse. Customization.\n8. **Storybook** — On various elements. Custom styling. Dark mode.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Works with Drupal form elements.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready. Utility component used by others.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
